<plot>A few days in the lives of Armelle and Matéo. At first sight, Matéo is only Armelle's son: isn't he only ten years old? But his mother can neither read nor write; all she can do is sign at the bottom of documents she does not understand. So Matéo is more than her kiddie : he helps her, protects her, is her accomplice. Thanks to Matéo, Armelle can hide her handicap. One day though, she gets a job offer...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?476947</url></doc>
